213
00:11:36,895 --> 00:11:39,498
<font color="white" size=".72c">
KAISER:

So this, this group here,</font>

214
00:11:39,531 --> 00:11:40,833
<font color="white" size=".72c">
these, these were the folks</font>

215
00:11:40,866 --> 00:11:45,471
<font color="white" size=".72c">
who had just been plumbing

