232
00:12:31,016 --> 00:12:33,218
<font color="white" size=".72c">
Before it's detected,</font>

233
00:12:33,251 --> 00:12:35,821
<font color="white" size=".72c">
instead of being

a solid particle,</font>

234
00:12:35,854 --> 00:12:39,224
