240
00:12:55,540 --> 00:12:56,575
<font color="white" size=".72c">
CARROLL:

It's like a wave</font>

241
00:12:56,608 --> 00:12:58,477
<font color="white" size=".72c">
of all those different

possibilities.</font>

242
00:12:58,510 --> 00:13:01,580
