266
00:14:03,942 --> 00:14:05,510
<font color="white" size=".72c">
KAISER:

Bonsoir.</font>

267
00:14:05,543 --> 00:14:08,380
<font color="white" size=".72c">
NARRATOR:

...he challenged the most vocal

supporter of these ideas:</font>

268
00:14:08,413 --> 00:14:13,619
