276
00:14:31,069 --> 00:14:32,604
<font color="white" size=".72c">
Bohr would have an answer.</font>

277
00:14:32,637 --> 00:14:34,306
<font color="white" size=".72c">
One of the observers said</font>

278
00:14:34,339 --> 00:14:35,908
<font color="white" size=".72c">
