294
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,789
<font color="white" size=".72c">
♪ ♪</font>

295
00:15:23,822 --> 00:15:28,860
<font color="white" size=".72c">
In 1933, with the Nazi Party

in power in Germany,</font>

296
00:15:28,893 --> 00:15:31,396
<font color="white" size=".72c">
Einstein chose to settle

