299
00:15:36,301 --> 00:15:39,004
<font color="white" size=".72c">
♪ ♪</font>

300
00:15:39,037 --> 00:15:42,174
<font color="white" size=".72c">
He recruited two physicists

to help him,</font>

301
00:15:42,207 --> 00:15:46,645
<font color="white" size=".72c">
