348
00:18:30,542 --> 00:18:35,947
<font color="white" size=".72c">
I put these two quantum dice

in my little cup,</font>

349
00:18:35,980 --> 00:18:39,384
<font color="white" size=".72c">
throw them.</font>

350
00:18:39,417 --> 00:18:43,255
<font color="white" size=".72c">
I look at them,

