360
00:19:13,518 --> 00:19:15,086
<font color="white" size=".72c">
It's really mind-boggling.</font>

361
00:19:15,119 --> 00:19:16,655
<font color="white" size=".72c">
♪ ♪</font>

362
00:19:16,688 --> 00:19:19,891
<font color="white" size=".72c">
NARRATOR:

How could two particles act

